{"tid":2069411,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"笑死！原來高加索窮國格魯吉亞護照都好用過中國護照","createTime":"2020-06-18T11:03:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T04:51:16.000Z","uid":120678,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c2603c4e5f7a41ad894cb6089ee2a77843c88ee5","tid":2069411,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T11:03:10.000Z","msg":"格魯吉亞 人均GDP US$4,285<br />\n中華人民共和國 人均GDP US$10,099<br />\n格魯吉亞人均GDP唔夠中國一半<br />\n<br />\n但睇下本passport免簽地區<br />\n格魯吉亞護照 114個國家及地區免簽證，好用程度全球排名50<br />\n中國護照 71個國家及地區免簽證，好用程度全球排名72<br />\n<br />\n格魯吉亞護照最正既係：2017年起有歐盟神根免簽，可免簽入境挪威、瑞士等全球最富裕國家<br />\n而且仲係180日內可以留90日既寬鬆條件，含金量即時大幅提升<br />\n另外格魯吉亞護照可以響大半個南美通行，包括巴西，甚至經濟程度較高既阿根廷同智利<br />\n至於中國？對唔住，差唔多全個南美都要簽證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果然，錢同經濟成就，未必一定可以為一個國家既人民帶來出遊時既便利<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource：<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Visa_requirements_for_Georgian_citizens\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FVisa_requirements_for_Georgian_citizens&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHpIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=98d6e2f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Visa_requirements_for_Georgian_citizens</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Visa_requirements_for_Chinese_citizens\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FVisa_requirements_for_Chinese_citizens&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHpIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=9cb34875\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Visa_requirements_for_Chinese_citizens</a>"},{"pid":"c456b7e6d765cd14007bce2ad8a61cc4fc3ee308","tid":2069411,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T11:04:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><